    "Applications in computed tomographyDeep computer vision has been heavily drawn upon for automated CT analysis.",
    "CT scans are volumetric scans; as a result, 3D CNNs are often leveraged.",
    "2D CNNs are also applied for problems where a single saggital, coronal, or axial image is sufficient for the target task.",
    "Vision transformers are increasingly being studied as well.",
    "Segmentation of organs and lesions are common examples of machine learning tasks in CT."
